{"tid":1550476,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"Telegram 公海Group注意！","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T17:50:49.000Z","uid":262971,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"07d9a7ba80b7c6f320677f7313ec7d178509ad8a","tid":1550476,"uid":262971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:15:31.000Z","msg":"為咗加強大家喺Telegram既私隱度<br />\n我地整咗個Bot可以<span style=\"color: red;\">限時銷毀群組訊息</span><br />\n咁萬一被人執到個電話, <br />\n都唔會俾人睇晒個Group既對話紀錄呀嘛<br />\n<br />\n用法好簡單,<br />\n任何Group Chat, 只要加入 <span style=\"color: red;\">@DelHistoryBot</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oFaXnEr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FoFaXnEr.png&h=e46f6a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後再畀個Bot Admin管理員權限<br />\n(只有admin先可以刪Message)<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/90E0DO0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F90E0DO0.png&h=767e02c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後只要用 /destroytimer &lt;分鐘&gt;<br />\n就可以set好每個訊息既自毀時間<br />\n例如一個鐘就係 /destroytimer 60<br />\n一日就係 /destroytimer 1440<br />\n(最多可以48小時, 呢個係telegram既限制)<br />\n想暫時熄咗佢, 就用 /destroyoff<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">注意: 如果set得太短, 可能D人未睇就delete咗</span><br />\n<br />\n&lt;Disclaimer&gt;<br />\n暫時測試緊, 唔排除間中有bug會delete唔到<br />\n建議只係秘密Group Chat, <br />\n完全唔想有history留底既Group先用<br />\n仲有, 呢個唔係俾Channel用, 係Group先用得<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到有需要既人"},{"pid":"8d2f3ec6c8ee35cc5936d64bdf81aa6c679df6e1","tid":1550476,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:15:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾